Sentinel v0.9.5.98

Title:
fix(data-guard): activate character re-ocr evidence by default

Summary:
- Auto-discovers screenshot directories and ZIP files for Ground Truth Character Re-OCR.
- Supports `551.zip` directly through `--screenshots-dir`.
- Adds explicit `--no-verify-characters` opt-out.
- Emits unresolved target evidence even when the OCR provider is unavailable.
- Adds regression tests for ZIP discovery and non-zero target emission.

Validation:
- pytest -q tests/smoke/test_targeted_character_reocr_97.py tests/smoke/test_character_reocr_98.py
- ground_truth_validator.py smoke run with lastwar_export.xlsx + 551.zip produced non-zero character_reocr_target_count.
- py_compile OK.

